{"tid":2009014,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企阿媽唔知點解開始好鍾意撩交嗌","createTime":"2020-05-09T12:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T04:27:02.000Z","uid":264067,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"364777929b856db0b8f0497b316e0b5cb4277a0d","tid":2009014,"uid":264067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"我阿媽今年53歲，大家都係黃絲，所以係政見上就好少鬧交。不過我阿媽係名副其實係一個港女。佢唔知點解年紀愈大就愈硬頸，唔聽人哋講野，但佢就會話返你轉頭點解唔聽佢講，話返我好硬頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最過份嘅係同佢鬧交會用啲好侮辱嘅說話，例如話我白癡仔，去做鴨呀之類嘅說話，明明以前佢都唔會咁話我。而且只係一啲好小事，佢就會同我鬧交。下下都要我氹番佢。今次又為咗一啲小事，又話我白癡，又話我唔用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果我嬲到就cut咗佢線。今次我就唔會理佢，叫佢自己慶祝母親節呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7606bc62970ef35809ac87792164dcabd24ce8d8","tid":2009014,"uid":125150,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"有無機會更年期？停經？如果係就要忍左幾年佢"},{"pid":"c519c6d509bbeb44cb628287de970f6071000180","tid":2009014,"uid":350003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:23:14.000Z","msg":"更年期"},{"pid":"852b77de6b25e9bb357966d3bed47d8fffc3d887","tid":2009014,"uid":199799,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"認真答你 更年期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃既就忍下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1212eeb1adf62ea9feaa9d88f50468e1ff30ab","tid":2009014,"uid":264067,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7606bc62970ef35809ac87792164dcabd24ce8d8","tid":2009014,"uid":125150,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"有無機會更年期？停經？如果係就要忍左幾年佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T